{"section": "3.8.4: Proving an inequality by induction.", "qid": 0, "input_type": "fieldset", "instructions": "<div class=\"activity-instructions\">\n <p>\n  Consider a proof of the following fact:\n </p>\n <div style=\"float: left;\">\n  <div class=\"zyblock\">\n   For all\n   <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n    n \u2265 4\n   </span>\n   ,\n   <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n    2\n    <sup>\n     n\n    </sup>\n    \u2265 n\n    <sup>\n     2\n    </sup>\n   </span>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div style=\"display: block; height: 0px; clear: both;\">\n </div>\n</div>\n", "question": "<div>\n <div class=\"text\">\n  What should be proven in the base case?\n </div>\n</div>", "correct_choice_index": 1, "choices": ["For n = 1, 2\n n\n\n \u2265 n\n 2", "For n = 4, 2\n n\n\n \u2265 n\n 2", "2\n k\n\n \u2265 k\n 2", "For every k \u2265 4,\n if 2\n k\n\n \u2265 k\n 2\n\n,\n then 2\n k+1\n\n \u2265 (k+1)\n 2"], "answer": "For n = 4, 2n \u2265 n2", "explanation": "<div aria-atomic=\"true\" class=\"explanation has-explanation correct\" role=\"alert\">\n <p class=\"message\">\n  Correct\n </p>\n The base case shows that the assertion holds for\n <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n  n = 4\n </span>\n .\n</div>\n"}